    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "At the end of the project, MacLeod estimates that about 1000 buildings will have been inventoried. They include all pre-Civil War structures and any of noteworthyities built since that time. As many as possible will be included in a book they hope to compile.",
      "bbox": {
